Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.82,0:01:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,氩同位素、镍、Ω钛\n骨骼的第一种构造材质…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.53,0:01:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镨、铽、polyethylene ampoule \N amido gel
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.24,0:01:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柔软的七个isalo筋肉、钯…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.74,0:02:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反应装置是由立方体结构\n组成方格状施电磁雷射投影迷彩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咕啡，早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咕啡，快起床
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.59,0:02:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咕啡，小要，要迟到了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咕啡…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,＃01  令人在意的那家伙是个士官
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.23,0:02:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（苏联伯力郊外）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.75,0:02:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.79,0:02:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我咬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不然就杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我咬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.56,0:02:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不然就杀…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙竟然做这么残忍的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:02:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.47,0:02:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是山岳地带，可以回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以回家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人型机动兵器AS(ArmSlave)…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘银的战士前来搭救公主了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗介，动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌军的增援来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,15秒就可以收容完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要对我怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相良…相良宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是旧式的M6
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在早就埋在永久冻土底下了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:13.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然用M9去对付\n敌人的雌鹿直升机耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雌鹿直升机？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没…没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若以M9的规格来看\n也不是办不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔，雌鹿直升机袭击美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将拦下来的雌鹿直升机巨大机体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一边撕裂一边朝向荒野掷去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡力林少校在找你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.42,0:06:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意见你直接去找他说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.53,0:06:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗介，你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.43,0:06:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:46.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你那张扭曲的嘴收起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不这样做\n你还是一副搞笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你讲话真是过份
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.90,0:06:54.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然朝着曾当过\n“The Tag”模特儿的我这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一箭射穿你的心，碰！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.62,0:07:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天我要让你\n抓我的背抓到不行…（暗指H）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说我是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个值得信赖的士官长…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.13,0:07:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.70,0:07:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅莉萨．毛士官长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克鲁兹．威巴士官
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相良宗介士官，现在报到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.68,0:07:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有任务
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鸟要？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.99,0:07:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她以后会是个美人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.26,0:07:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照片是四年前拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.89,0:07:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位少女现在16岁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.56,0:07:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么现在的照片呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KGB以及其它的不特定多数组织\n计划绑架她的可能性很高
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.27,0:07:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本政府就不必说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:08:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不能让千鸟要本人察觉\n并前去保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.77,0:08:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以你们三个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:03.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有三个人？太难了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.11,0:08:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是如此才要你们去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.51,0:08:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要求配备B等级装备
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,许可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:12.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,M9一架，配备最低限度武装
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外带两个外部蓄电器去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这并非不可能的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先要准备伪造文件跟大头照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照相机，照相机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文件？照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:27.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少校，是什么文件？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还用说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是转学申请书
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.95,0:08:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在舰内搜集来了一些\n日本高中生应该会带的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗，这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是保险套喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.03,0:08:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但为什么高中生要用这种东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:03.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑开心一点，宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，你又在装傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个色狼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.51,0:09:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也曾经用过几次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.85,0:09:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在丛林里遗失水壶时可以用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.75,0:09:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以装满整整一公升的水呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，秘银
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:33.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字用真名没关系吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正在那个国家也没有我的户籍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.54,0:09:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯，是没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是，真的不要紧吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰蕾莎很担心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上校大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也没办法，因为是重要的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:09:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那个问题啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要起飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咕啡，咕啡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安，小要，要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的天使因为低血压
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.49,0:11:07.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以早上很难叫起来…是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一早就看到女高中生的晨浴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.70,0:11:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋，快点给我出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,声纹检查开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.55,0:11:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请念出姓名、阶级、辨识号码
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.72,0:11:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克鲁兹威巴士官，B-3127
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认是克鲁兹士官无误
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,0750时，天使要去上学了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关闭舱门
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始调整为模式4
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双边角3.5
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.40,0:11:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.34,0:11:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,执行模式4
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:54.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,BMSA3.5，完成
