Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“墨樵的成功哲学，历史篇”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“活得像诸葛孔明一样”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.97,0:12:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“海豚们的警告”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:12:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“再见，谢谢你们，鱼儿”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真特殊的嗜好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了，你可以走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，打开书包
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.42,0:13:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.26,0:13:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.49,0:13:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天那是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么老爸是设计师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友在J联盟踢球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.67,0:13:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你又算哪根葱啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不能多谈些\n可以提高彼此格调的话题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.71,0:13:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是孔明的一生\n喂，等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是甲烷水合物的\n有效利用法之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.28,0:13:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.65,0:13:43.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么说得也是，恭子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.72,0:13:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是你介绍的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.29,0:13:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为人家拜托我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是不是这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有人拜托你把我卖到国外去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.13,0:13:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也会照做吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.93,0:13:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了了，你这个臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:14:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转学第一天就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种玩具我要没收
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，那不是玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它装填了高杀伤力的爆裂弹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.21,0:14:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌，是军事狂耶，好恶心…\n请别碰板机，一旦爆发会出人命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.05,0:14:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好，我知道了，你放心吧\n嗯，说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的偶像竟然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，大家安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要介绍新同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军事狂，碰！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么相良同学，做个自我介绍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是相良宗介士官
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.58,0:14:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨鲁喀绶司介肯什？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.21,0:14:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是“羽柴筑前守秀吉”那种感觉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“士官”是指军队的士官吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安静
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.79,0:14:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听人家讲完
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.99,0:14:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相良同学也不要再开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.63,0:15:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.53,0:15:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫相良宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.30,0:15:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思，请把“士官”忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.44,0:15:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唱首歌来听听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.90,0:15:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样而已吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是，就只有这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.27,0:15:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人想问问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我，相良同学是从哪里转来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:21.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿富汗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黎巴嫩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.62,0:15:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柬埔寨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊拉克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.92,0:15:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥伦比亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:29.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原…原来在外国\n住了相当长的时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.46,0:15:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴趣是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会是模型枪吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，是钓鱼跟看书
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都看什么书呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.07,0:15:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是，主要是技术书类与专门杂志
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我常看詹氏年鉴之类的书籍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.74,0:15:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“佣兵战场”\n也蛮有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有订哈里斯出版社的\n“人型机动兵器AS(ArmSlave) 月刊”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了，我也看过日本的“AS Fan”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,书的内容比我想象的还要高水平
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令我相当感动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是本很好的杂志
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近比较迷海洋相关的书籍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.39,0:16:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国海军学会出版社的新刊\n大约买了10本
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在睡前…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.17,0:16:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请忘掉我刚才说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.27,0:16:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…有喜欢的歌手吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,角川五郎跟素颜女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.27,0:16:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人愿意跟我换班吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.71,0:16:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙真的很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.88,0:17:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽是说些莫名其妙的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.38,0:17:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下课在教室和走廊间走来走去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.12,0:17:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种沉不住气的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.99,0:17:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到就觉得烦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你不要看就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没有在看那个军事迷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且，而且啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.07,0:17:21.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔会跟他的眼睛相对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一直看着这边耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.40,0:17:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然他会装着一副\n“偶然不小心看到”的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后把视线移开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是根本就破绽百出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:29.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊，真是恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.24,0:17:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法，因为小要长得很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.85,0:17:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.48,0:17:35.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是跟那没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那根本就是变态的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总觉得小要一直在讲\n相良的坏话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.39,0:17:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.36,0:17:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊，你这么在意他吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦好啦\n这个话题就到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:17:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.18,0:17:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（垒球社）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.45,0:18:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.22,0:18:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,色狼，不要看后面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.06,0:18:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧，小要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看啦，都擦破皮了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于粗暴的行为，我在此谢罪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.07,0:18:33.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我绝对不是想要\n危害你或是你的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你到底是想干嘛啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.64,0:18:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.64,0:18:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有资格知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.11,0:18:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,资格？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么资格啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.11,0:18:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能说，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相良，你来这里干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在之前的学校\n也曾参加过你们这种社团
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对于过去的表现还蛮有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:58.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对体力也有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雇用我相信对你们没有害处
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.40,0:19:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1，2…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（女子垒球社）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差点踢到老爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还被狗吠了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.45,0:19:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用手轻碰了一下补习班的大楼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果窗户的玻璃裂开了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.79,0:19:25.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把教室里的小学生吓得半死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.26,0:19:27.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是累死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小要有电话喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦，是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯，对啊，转学生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.28,0:19:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是折迭椅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看也知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手铐的钥匙孔被转向手肘那边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.83,0:20:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯，手法相当厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜这个之赐\n在泉川车站买票时真的很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.93,0:20:10.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯，是个奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.57,0:20:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.17,0:20:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是，虽然有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对，应该说是虽然很奇怪\n不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯，是个很有趣的人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说你很有趣喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我就不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总比被说成无聊的家伙要好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.56,0:20:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来\n跟她在学校的印象差很多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.53,0:20:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相较于现在\n她更加激动、更具有攻击性
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.83,0:20:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个很有趣的人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.37,0:20:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我似乎没被千鸟要讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.74,0:20:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗介，你看起来蛮高兴的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.84,0:20:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:24.14,edch,NTP,0,0,0,,在\N心\N中\N绽\N开\N着\N一\N朵\N小\N花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:35.79,edch,NTP,0,0,0,,你\N给\N我\N的\N那\N朵\N不\N会\N枯\N萎\N的\N花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.84,0:21:42.84,edch,NTP,0,0,0,,让\N我\N不\N再\N畏\N惧\N相\N信\N他\N人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.84,0:21:49.64,edch,NTP,0,0,0,,因\N此\N变\N得\N更\N坚\N强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.29,0:21:55.94,edch,NTP,0,0,0,,能\N与\N你\N相\N遇\N\N真\N的\N很\N高\N兴
